init_text:
Once upon a time there was an old mother pig who had one hundred little pigs and not enough food to feed them. So when they were old enough, she sent them out into the world to seek their fortunes. You know the story about the first three little pigs. This is a story about the 92nd little pig.

The 92nd little pig built a house out of depleted uranium. And the wolf was like, "dude."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: So the wolf huffed and puffed and blew down every other house in the neighborhood, but he was unable to blow down the 92nd little pig

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Then he came across one that looked promising.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: So the wolf went to his dojo, took some deep breaths, and then attempted to blow down the house.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: And after a while they needed to take a break.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They got into a circle, held hands and began blowing as hard as they could.
